underlying_goal: Initialize a read-only exploration agent and confirm its understanding of project state and constraints.
primary_success: The agent integrated information from the git status to provide an up-to-date summary of the project state, in addition to its read-only capabilities.
brief_summary: An excellent warmup session. The agent correctly identified the project, noted the current pending file changes from the git status, reiterated its read-only constraints, and listed the tools it would use for exploration.
